                     <interp inst="t18020918-42-person350" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn. - I was with Mr. Cecil; I saw the prisoner in the act of putting the handkerchief in his bosom.</p>
               <p>Mr. Cecil. I am sure it is my handkerchief.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's defence. I picked up the handkerchief on the pavement; there were a great number of people collected. <rs id="t18020918-42-verdict223" type="verdictDescription">
